  "text": "The second verification involved problems of interference between controllers. We adapted and simplified the solution proposed by Evans & Treharne [CITATION_1] for verifying the non-interference of controllers. We exploit the additional knowledge given by modularity links at the B level to naturally deduce non-interference properties from the modularity links.",
